# StatusBadge

`TxStatusBadge` renders compact status text with a tone icon, optional platform icon, and a normalized `statusKey` mapping for permission or backend status enums.

Reviewed against `packages/tuffex/packages/components/src/status-badge/src/types.ts`, `TxStatusBadge.vue`, and `status-badge.test.ts`.

